Strange (01 - 04) (2010) (Minutemen) 


No longer Sorcerer Supreme of the Marvel Universe, Stephen Strange must dicover a new path to fulfillment and enlightenment. Unfortuantely, that path leads through a bizarre, terrifying gauntlet of magical menaces--and if the former Master of the Mystic Arts is going to survive the journey, he'll need some assistance--in the form of a brand-new student!
